Package: shinyscholar
Version: 0.2.2
Date: 2024-12-03
Title: A template for creating modular reproducible Shiny applications
Description: Creates a skeleton shiny application that is modular, reproducible,
    can be saved and loaded and meets academic standards for attribution. Using 
    shinyscholar encourages best practices in software development. Includes 
    functions for automating repetitive development tasks. 'shinyscholar' 
    was forked from 'wallace'. 
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Simon E. H.", "Smart", email = "simon.smart@cantab.net", 
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")))
